	(drbg_ctr_df): Ditto.
	(drbg_hmac_update): Ditto.
	(drbg_hmac_generate): Replace drgb_hmac by drbg_hash.
	(drbg_hash_df): Ditto.
	(drbg_hash_process_addtl): Ditto.
	(drbg_hash_hashgen): Ditto.
