	Add Intel PCLMUL implementations of CRC algorithms.
	+ commit 5d601dd57fcb41aa2015ab655fd6fc51537da667
	* cipher/Makefile.am: Add 'crc-intel-pclmul.c'.
	* cipher/crc-intel-pclmul.c: New.
