	+ commit be2238f68abcc6f2b4e8c38ad9141376ce622a22
	* cipher/Makefile.am: Add 'sha1-ssse3-amd64.c'.
	* cipher/sha1-ssse3-amd64.c: New.
	* cipher/sha1.c (USE_SSSE3): New.
