	(sha1_init) [USE_SSSE3]: Initialize 'use_ssse3'.
	(transform): Rename to...
	(_transform): this.
	(transform): New.
	* configure.ac [host=x86_64]: Add 'sha1-ssse3-amd64.lo'.

